"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-08-07-paris-2024-olympics-ofili-reflects-on-disappointing-outing-in-womens-200m-final\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  Favour Ofili has moved on from the disappointment of failing to win a medal in the women's 200m event at the ongoing Paris 2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 161, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ofili finished in sixth position in the final of the event on Tuesday night, clocking 22.24s.\", \"from\": 163, \"to\": 256, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"USA's Gabrielle Thomas won gold with a time of 21.83s, Julien Alfred took silver with 22.08s, while Brittany Brown went home with bronze in a time of 22.20s.\", \"from\": 258, \"to\": 415, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 258, \"end\": 261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.502072546845443, \"rank\": 0.589472076790547, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 264, \"end\": 280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabrielle Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabrielle_Thomas\"}, {\"begin\": 358, \"end\": 372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittany_Brown\", \"score\": 0.999999998668045, \"rank\": 1.3319712393318685e-09, \"text\": \"Brittany Brown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittany_Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brittany_Brown\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 21-year-old, who was making her debut at the Olympics, took to the social media to thank her coach.\", \"from\": 417, \"to\": 520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tried to be mentally ready regardless of the shocking news I took a few days back.\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 605, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I gave it my all from lane 9.\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 635, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If it was easy, everyone would be doing it,\\\" she wrote on X.\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 696, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Thank you, Coach Shaver.\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 723, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Having you around made everything a lot easier for me.\\\"\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 779, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ofili is now looking forward to competing in the women's 400x100m.\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 847, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Next 4\\u00d7100.\", \"from\": 848, \"to\": 860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On God,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Transfer: He will be a genius - Neymar hails Chelsea-bound forward  Transfer: Best Brazilian born player I have seen - Branco hails Chelsea-bound star  Paris 2024 Olympics: Nigeria's dismal performance worries enthusiasts  Paris 2024 Olympics: D'Tigress' Wakama wins Best Coach award  Paris 2024 Olympics: Brume vows to  bounce back from disappointing outing  Paris 2024 Olympics: Sports Minister apologises to Nigerians after disastrous outing  Paris 2024 Olympics: Team Nigeria officially finishes without single medal  Paris 2024 Olympics: Nigeria's last medal hope Reuben crashes out in Wrestling  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1055, \"end\": 1062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9784403991797059, \"rank\": 0.019058698405041374, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 1425, \"en